--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/twisted/trial/newsfragments/12390.bugfix
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+twisted.trial.unittest.TestCase.addCleanup will cause the test to fail if the returned deferred is not resolved before the test's timeout.
